# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
# ITBrains E-Commerce — .gitignore
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Maven ###
target/
*.jar
*.war
!.mvn/wrapper/maven-wrapper.jar
!**/src/main/**/target/
!**/src/test/**/target/

### STS ###
.apt_generated
.classpath
.factorypath
.project
.settings
.springBeans
.sts4-cache

### IntelliJ IDEA ###
.idea/
*.iws
*.iml
*.ipr

### NetBeans ###
/nbproject/private/
/nbbuild/
/dist/
/nbdist/
/.nb-gradle/
build/
!**/src/main/**/build/
!**/src/test/**/build/

### VS Code ###
.vscode/

### OS ###
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

### Environment — şifrələr GitHub-a getməsin! ###
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

### Sensitive configuration ###
src/main/resources/application.properties
src/main/resources/application-prod.properties
src/main/resources/application-local.properties

### Logs ###
*.log
logs/
spring-shell.log

### Docker ###
docker-compose.override.yml

### Uploads — qovluğu saxla, məzmunu yox ###
uploads/*
!uploads/.gitkeep
